1. *Stigao* sam na vreme. (I arrived on time.)
2. Nadam se da ćemo *stići* do Beograda pre mraka. (I hope we will arrive in Belgrade before dark.)
3. Kada *stignete* u grad, molim vas javite mi. (When you arrive in the city, please let me know.)
4. Juče sam *stigao* na posao i odmah seo za računar. (Yesterday, I arrived at work and immediately sat down at the computer.)
5. Ako *stignemo* na vreme, moći ćemo da uhvatimo poslednji voz. (If we arrive on time, we will be able to catch the last train.)
6. Molim vas da *stignete* na aerodrom najmanje sat vremena pre leta. (Please arrive at the airport at least an hour before the flight.)
7. Uvek *stižem* na vreme na sastanke. (I always arrive on time for meetings.)
8. Da li si *stigao* da završiš sve zadatke? (Did you manage to finish all the tasks?)
9. Nadam se da će moja poruka *stići* do tebe na vreme. (I hope my message will reach you on time.)
10. Nećemo *stići* do cilja ako nastavimo ovim tempom. (We won't reach our goal if we continue at this pace.)